# Security Policy

## Reporting a Vulnerability
If you discover a security issue, please email us at **security@betteroptionforall.org**.  
We will respond within 72 hours and aim to resolve issues quickly.

## Supported Versions
- Current `main` branch
- Latest stable release

## Data Ethics
We are committed to protecting user data. All personal information collected will be anonymized for analysis and used only with informed consent. Sensitive data will not be stored in this repository.
